title: MahJong Suite 2008 v5.1
description:
MahJong Suite is a high-quality collection of MahJong
solitaire games.
Each MahJong game has millions of possible shuffles to play,
so the game remains fresh no matter how many times you play.
Enjoy the detailed statistics of each game with graphs, 3D
charts (pies and bars) and tables to estimate your skill
level (by total, current session, series of wins and losses,
players&#039; games won, players&#039; score, hi-scores...), statistics
for All Games, Won games, Not Won games, Over Average, Under
Average, Not Played...
For MahJong lovers, MahJong Suite is a guaranteed pleasure.
Each of the games is fun and exciting and will keep you
entertained for hours. If you like MahJong games, then you&#039;ll
want to add MahJong Suite to your collection!
